  {
    "id": "closing",
    "narration": "So the simple flow is: Start in Builder. Choose the presenter, audience, scan color, and goals. Use the right side to guide the live conversation. Go to Script for the full talk track. Go to AI Prompt if you want AI to rewrite or extend it. Go to Guardrails to keep the language safe. Go to Pipeline to check client progression. Go to Tests to make sure the app logic is working. That's the app: it helps someone run a smarter scanner conversation without guessing what to say.",
    "actions": [
